2916Ajjhattārammaṇo dhammo ajjhattārammaṇassa dhammassa vipākapaccayena paccayo…pe…  āhārapaccayena paccayo…  indriyapaccayena paccayo…  jhānapaccayena paccayo…  maggapaccayena paccayo…  sampayuttapaccayena paccayo…  atthipaccayena paccayo…  natthipaccayena paccayo…  vigatapaccayena paccayo…  avigatapaccayena paccayo.
